	<p>An Enchanter who has been Charming for awhile (the spell, not personality) can mitigate a lot of risk.  And you know what helps? (LDON, Trials)....<br />
<br />
Having another slower in the group.  Trust me I speak from experience.  <br />
<br />
I have to second the Necro call. Holy cow. <br />
<br />
Quick - name something a Necro CAN'T do?<br />
<br />
Mez? Nope.<br />
Charm? Nope.<br />
Heal? Nope.<br />
Slow? Nope.<br />
Snare? Nope.<br />
DPS? Puhleez.<br />
REZ? Nope they can do that too.<br />
<br />
The only thing a Necro "can't do" is tank.  Or so I thought.<br />
<br />
Then a Necro on our server soloed a named in a LDON HARD. (Guk Theme which helped admittedly)<br />
<br />
A good Shaman is great - a good Necro is ungodly.</p>
	
	
	
